data.description: This home is a must see! The living room has a large space for entertaining and a cozy, beautiful fireplace. The kitchen has had a gorgeous upgrade to the cabinetry with ample counter space. The dining room has a large beautiful window that allows nature light to come through showcasing the beautiful greenery outside to be seen. All rooms are spacious with wood flooring and unique brick flooring. The back yard has beautiful greenery all around creating your own oasis in the middle of the city. Conveniently located near schools, the University, shopping and dining.
